# Secrets - SOPS Configuration
# Allow encrypted files and templates, but ignore plain secrets
secrets/*
!secrets/.gitkeep
!secrets/*.example
!secrets/*.template
!secrets/README.md
!secrets/*.enc           # Allow encrypted files (SOPS)
